{"tid":681624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[飛雞要幫忙止血呢] 乘客爆尿管「賓周流住血」飛往三藩市 港航被指延誤求助","createTime":"2018-05-28T07:54:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T14:20:42.000Z","uid":54373,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7f9f9e767a6c51335fc2feaaf89791b8fd69b069","tid":681624,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T07:54:32.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】網上流傳港航日前一班飛往美國三藩市航機上，有使用導尿管的男乘客，如廁時疑誤將尿管弄斷，大量流血，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">空姐循血跡搜索揭發事件</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，機長及高級機艙事務長被指延誤通報救助，有協助救援的護士要求從速致電醫療熱線不果，最終乘客需「流住血」飛往三藩市。本網已向港航查詢，正等候回覆。<br />\n<br />\n事件於上周一發生，有人於Facebook 專頁「KA Secrets」發文，指該班機上並無衛星電話，需靠駕駛室衛星通信，但當時人員並無即時向Medlink通報求助，有協助的護士見事態嚴重，「出聲」要求從速致電，「當事人同佢太太好驚，因為流咗好多血&hellip;&hellip;最後個客係流住血去三藩市」。<br />\n<br />\n留言指出，「因為有travel companion onboard 唔想架機divert」、「係兩位in charge既處理手法，置乘客安全為次要，6day SFO享樂為主要。」質疑有人帶同親友同行，及為「享受」飛長途線的休息「假期」，以致不願通報。<br />\n<br />\n亦有消息指，事故發生後，有關洗手間未有按日常做法封閉，惹起感染危機憂慮。"},{"pid":"7e9f603f02b98928525ba1859acd36d162517ce6","tid":681624,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:01:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗起都痛啊"},{"pid":"16eb8e96f31cac56bd9b2d0c6006bd3ef16daf8a","tid":681624,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee8501e9b3a03591f23c3395f51b0f905c60da8b","tid":681624,"uid":183666,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:53:18.000Z","msg":"賓周流住血<br />\n<br />\n咁似乜登啲會員名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"894ae824d5b13c39215eec999dcfe4f3124cd83f","tid":681624,"uid":28831,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:55:00.000Z","msg":"支那公司做法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f340572478f6b5eee600fa7ebd724a3d6f49d38","tid":681624,"uid":39628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:59:59.000Z","msg":"見到空姐可能加速下體流更多血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dec027c57f7a149c467a2af3b744542a91547ef","tid":681624,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f340572478f6b5eee600fa7ebd724a3d6f49d38","tid":681624,"uid":39628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:59:59.000Z","msg":"見到空姐可能加速下體流更多血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T09:10:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6017a64a8584f43a9ed7ff77fc0434b4bcb93c0","tid":681624,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T09:12:52.000Z","msg":"可能有海航啲姨媽姑嗲喺飛機度。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(連登仔好多都唔識海航係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"3e5b317113a9214b80c751d388badb85d58b775b","tid":681624,"uid":85629,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T10:54:23.000Z","msg":"插住尿喉都要去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77bae2683e5bf22b531592807b5fb615d514fdb8","tid":681624,"uid":44105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T13:50:57.000Z","msg":"支那公司係咁慳"},{"pid":"5f84d40c7a71c9437a9c596a7c1223418bb4facf","tid":681624,"uid":128087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3e5b317113a9214b80c751d388badb85d58b775b","tid":681624,"uid":85629,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T10:54:23.000Z","msg":"插住尿喉都要去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"